Thierry Frémont https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thierry_Fr%C3%A9mont 0 Thierry Frémont (born 24 July 1962) is a French actor. He has appeared in more than 65 films and television shows since 1984. He starred in the 1991 film Fortune Express, which was entered into the 41st Berlin International Film Festival. Thierry_Frémont ( born 24_July_1962 ) is a_French_actor .
